{"tid":1464450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"只接受單一意見 先係對運動嘅最大危害","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:02:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:55:38.000Z","uid":105995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9cb3e90aa310bac29cae40ffd56a88e2a04bf868","tid":1464450,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:02:23.000Z","msg":"記唔記得 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">兄弟爬山 各有各做</span></span><br />\n<br />\n宜家對面進化左 識得去連登攞料 識得搞分化<br />\n<br />\n我地和只接受單一意見 一定要傾到分出勝負<br />\n<br />\n咁我地行動只有一種方向 <br />\n<br />\n失去探索 改良 同進化嘅能力<br />\n<br />\n對面好易捉路同應對 因為我地思維單一 對面簡直係睇住食<br />\n<br />\n咁運動先係玩完<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我哋應該珍惜相反嘅意見 探索新嘅方向 不分化 兄弟爬山</span>"},{"pid":"b09d98497c31fa63ee12f403e77f2c52ee024967","tid":1464450,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:55:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}